/* Windows resource script for Announcer.exe.
 *
 * Embeds applogo.ico as the executable's primary icon, which Windows uses
 * for the taskbar, Alt+Tab, Explorer file listing, and the title bar. The
 * wxFrame:SetIcons() call in Announcer.wx.lua attaches PNG icons at runtime
 * for the wx-side widgets, but the OS-side taskbar uses ONLY the embedded
 * .exe resource - hence we need both. Closes the second half of
 * luadch-ng/announcer#63.
 *
 * IDI_ICON1 is the lowest-numbered ICON ordinal; Windows shell picks the
 * first ICON resource by ordinal as the "main" icon for the .exe.
 */
IDI_ICON1 ICON "applogo.ico"
